comments: I didn't use paper I just used repetition to remember the words. Overall I managed to learn what words were for what shape but what threw me at the end was how to know which colour shape to choose, I didn't realise the words distinguished colour as well as shape so I think I didn't teach myself that bit. I just kept repeating in my head wopico circle, zettyco bang shape etc. I think I got the overall alien words but not the variants of them. I am surprised what I did manage to learn in a short amount of time though.
